<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Sleep Well, My Whole World 🤍💤</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #1a2a49 0%, #0c1428 60%, #000 100%);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        
        /* Night Sky Scenery */
        .stars {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 60vh;
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .star {
            position: absolute;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: twinkle var(--duration) ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes twinkle {
            0% { opacity: 0.1; transform: scale(0.8); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }
        
        .moon {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10%;
            right: 15%;
            font-size: 30px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 200, 0.5));
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* Cozy Room Art */
        .room-base {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 40vh;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1f1228 0%, #150a1b 100%);
            border-top: 4px solid #331d42;
            z-index: 3;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }

        /* Boy and Bed Scene */
        .boy-bed-container {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.4));
            position: relative;
            animation: cozySway 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .letter-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            left: 10px;
            animation: letterWiggle 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes cozySway {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-5px) rotate(-1deg); }
        }
        @keyframes letterWiggle {
            0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: rotate(5deg) scale(1.1); }
        }

        /* Interactive Card */
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 350px;
            z-index: 10;
            background: rgba(20, 35, 60, 0.8);
            padding: 40px 25px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            animation: cardAppear 1s ease-out;
        }
        @keyframes cardAppear {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px) scale(0.9); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
        }

        .icon-header {
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .question {
            color: #d1d9e6;
            font-size: 19px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #6c5ce7, #a29bfe);
            color: white;
            height: 55px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 250px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 28px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.4);
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        /* The Long Love Letter Screen */
        .letter-screen {
            display: none;
            text-align: left;
            z-index: 15;
            background: rgba(10, 20, 40, 0.95);
            padding: 45px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            max-width: 380px;
            width: 90%;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            border: 1px solid rgba(162, 155, 254, 0.2);
            overflow-y: auto;
            max-height: 85vh;
        }
        
        .letter-screen::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 5px; }
        .letter-screen::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #6c5ce7; border-radius: 10px; }

        .letter-screen h2 { 
            color: #a29bfe; 
            font-size: 26px; 
            margin-bottom: 25px; 
            text-align: center;
        }
        .letter-screen p { 
            color: #f0f0f0; 
            font-size: 16px; 
            line-height: 1.8; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            font-weight: 400;
            text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        
        .ily-reply {
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding-top: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #d1d9e6;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Stars Sky -->
    <div class="stars" id="starContainer"></div>
    
    <!-- Moon -->
    <div class="moon">🌙✨</div>

    <!-- Initial Asking Card -->
    <div class="container" id="mainCard">
        <div class="icon-header">😴💙</div>
        <h1 class="question">Before you sleep, I just want to tell my baby...</h1>
        <button class="btn" onclick="openLetter()">How much I love you 👉🏻👈🏻</button>
    </div>

    <!-- The Long Love Letter (Opens after tap) -->
    <div class="letter-screen" id="letterScreen">
        <h2>My Whole World 🤍🧸</h2>
        <p>I wish I could wrap my arms around you right now, pull you so close, and just feel your steady breathing against me. Since I can’t be there physically to kiss your forehead and tuck you in, please close your eyes and imagine this letter is my hug.</p>
        <p>My love, you make every part of my life so much better just by existing. You are the most beautiful, caring, and strongest girl I have ever known. Even on your hardest days, your strength makes me so unbelievably proud. Looking at you makes me realize that I have everything I have ever wanted right in front of me.</p>
        <p>I don’t just love you for who you are; I love you for how you make me feel—so safe, so inspired, and so full of happiness. Loving you is the easiest and most important decision I have ever made. I am completely and endlessly yours, now and forever. Sleep peacefully, my precious baby. You are loved more than you could ever imagine. 🤍</p>
        
        <!-- Her Reply -->
        <div class="ily-reply">
            <span style="font-size: 20px; vertical-align: middle;">👧🏻☁️</span> "I love you too"
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Room and Bed Art -->
    <div class="room-base">
        <div class="boy-bed-container">
            <span style="position: absolute; top: -10px; font-size: 20px;">✍🏻</span>
            <span class="letter-icon">✉️</span>
            👦🏻🛏️
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Generate twinkling stars
        const container = document.getElementById('starContainer');
        for (let i = 0; i < 40; i++) {
            const star = document.createElement('div');
            star.classList.add('star');
            const size = Math.random() * 2 + 1;
            star.style.width = size + 'px';
            star.style.height = size + 'px';
            star.style.top = Math.random() * 60 + 'vh';
            star.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
            star.style.setProperty('--duration', (Math.random() * 2 + 1) + 's');
            container.appendChild(star);
        }

        function openLetter() {
            document.getElementById('mainCard').style.display = 'none';
            document.getElementById('letterScreen').style.display = 'block';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
